title: This Strange Realm Of Mine
description: This Strange Realm Of Mine is a First Person Shooter mixed with poetry and psychological horror. Graphic style is 3D mixed with pixel art.- Old-School FPS action- Explore Fantastical Worlds- Puzzles- Story heavy- Poetry- Varying gameplay- Original Soundtrack (Included)Start off by creating yourself, then die. In REALM you explore your afterlife. On your quest you'll find characters in different situations, with their problems and thoughts
